OL,3,C'We've had to make some difficult
OL,4,Cdecisions': Funding pulled for toddler
OL,5,Cgroup
OL,7,FA free toddler playgroup that runs
OL,8,Fsessions for hundreds of children
OL,9,Facross Jersey every week is set to
OL,10,Fclose.
OL,12,FThe Move More toddler play service
OL,13,Fprovided by Jersey Sport will end next
OL,14,Fmonth following a review.
OL,16,FIt found that the sessions no longer
OL,17,Ffall within their remit - but it has
OL,18,Fleft some parents disappointed.
