OL,5,Cgroup
OL,7,FAnother parent stressed how valuable
OL,8,Fthe service was: "It's a safe
OL,9,Fenvironment where the children can
OL,10,Fcome and play, be with children their
OL,11,Fown age, and the fact that they go to
OL,12,Fvarious venues across the islands
OL,13,Fmeans it's accessible to all."
OL,15,FThe sessions cost #70,000 a year and
OL,16,Fafter an internal review, the
OL,17,Fgovernment-funded body said the
OL,18,Fservice does not fall within their
OL,19,Fremit of sport and is opting to
OL,20,Freallocate funding to other projects.
