OL,7,FDavid Kennedy, CEO of Jersey Sport,
OL,8,Fsays: "We know that there are other
OL,9,Fbaby and toddler groups out there that
OL,10,Fpeople can go to... we're making sure
OL,11,Fwe narrow our focus somewhat to impact
OL,12,Fthe sporting community.
OL,14,F"We can't be a hundred things for a
OL,15,Fhundred people."
