OL,3,C'We've had to make some difficult
OL,4,Cdecisions': Funding pulled for toddler
OL,5,Cgroup
OL,7,FKennedy told ITV News the Review of
OL,8,FSport and Physical Activity in Jersey
OL,9,F- published last year - was "extremely
OL,10,Fcritical" of Jersey Sport, citing the
OL,11,F"level of strategic drift Jersey sport
OL,12,Fhad over a number of years."
OL,14,FHe explains: "One of the
OL,15,Frecommendations was to review our
OL,16,Fprogrammes, we've done that and as a
OL,17,Fresult, we've had to make some
OL,18,Fdifficult decisions - of which Toddler
OL,19,FPlay was one of them.
