OL,3,C'We've had to make some difficult
OL,4,Cdecisions': Funding pulled for toddler
OL,5,Cgroup
OL,7,F"We'll be using our resources to focus
OL,8,Fon impactful projects."
OL,10,FChildminder Rachel Le Couilliard has
OL,11,Fretaliated to the decision, saying:
OL,12,F"What do they actually think
OL,13,Fconstitutes sports? Because playing
OL,14,Fwith balls and making big movements, I
OL,15,Fwould say constitutes a sport and it's
OL,16,Fage-appropriate for those children."
OL,18,FDeputy Louise Doublet, Chair of the
OL,19,FHealth and Social Security Panel, was
OL,20,Falso critical of the move.
