OL,3,C'We've had to make some difficult
OL,4,Cdecisions': Funding pulled for toddler
OL,5,Cgroup
OL,7,FShe says: "Any money spent on young
OL,8,Fchildren has a massive return on that
OL,9,Finvestment down the years - so we must
OL,10,Ftake a long-term view of this.
OL,12,F"I've just spoken to our St. Saviour
OL,13,FConstable. He and I share an
OL,14,Funderstanding of the importance of
OL,15,Fchildren's play and he has said that
OL,16,Fhe will consider giving some funding
OL,17,Fto this project."
OL,19,FDeputy Doublet has encouraged people
OL,20,Fto share their views with Jersey Sport
OL,21,Fand their local parishes.
